{"tid":39054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懶理申訴專員公署裁定 半島電視台報道港府拒網媒採訪","createTime":"2016-12-14T10:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T13:13:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2784701c6975354fa0c96609703aae5fdedc54","tid":39054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161214/56045886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161214%2F56045886&d=kUOmVkoz4SyC5MjAHsnYIgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=bcb277ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161214%2F56045886&h=79cdbc26\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161214/56045886</a><br />\n<br />\n記協早前向申訴專員公署投訴，指政府新聞處拒絕多家網媒進入選舉委員會新聞中心採訪，公署裁定投訴成立；但早前選委會選舉中央點票站，政府仍拒絕讓多間網媒記者進入傳媒區採訪，包括《立場新聞》、HKFP等；半島電視台周三就事件作報道。<br />\n<br />\n半島電視台跟隨英文網媒HKFP編輯總監鄭樂捷嘗試進入傳媒採訪區，最終鄭無法取得採訪證，只可在公眾區採訪，鄭表示經常難以進入政府大樓或獲得新聞稿；政府指有關做法是要保障安全和避免現場太擠擁。<br />\n報道又指，如在美國大選期間，網上經常流傳假新聞，記協副主席任美貞認為要開放予網媒作自由採訪固然會引發爭議，但這不是完全扼殺網媒的有力理據。"},{"pid":"a657aa52b9363b8934981a87005d9afdbb8b315d","tid":39054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b6f3248493b714339a844856e0c84ce7eb989a","tid":39054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef130593ecdd3b699b59ea9e069903f6a7c3b05d","tid":39054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}